# About ratl.ai

# About ratl.ai

- ratl.ai is an AI-powered autonomous agentic software testing platform that leverages large language models to generate, execute, and validate test cases with minimal human intervention. It aims to revolutionize the software testing landscape by automating the entire testing lifecycle, from test case generation to execution and reporting.
- It is an in-house product of Fynd
- At Fynd, I work on ratl.ai, building and shipping features end-to-end, collaborating closely with cross-functional teams including product managers, designers, and other engineers to deliver high-quality software solutions.
